---
import Pheader from "../components/common/Pheader.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-300">
    <Pheader text="PRIVACY POLICY" align="center" />
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-pink-500 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: June 14, 2025</p>
      
      <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl mb-8 border border-gray-700">
        <p class="text-lg">
          This Privacy Policy explains how I handle your personal information when you interact with my 
          portfolio website and any associated services. As an independent developer, I'm committed to 
          protecting your privacy rights.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Interpretation and Definitions -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Key Terms</h2>
          
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Portfolio</strong> refers to my personal developer portfolio website.</li>
            <li><strong>I/Me/My</strong> refers to Alberto Plaza Montes, the owner of this portfolio.</li>
            <li><strong>You/Your</strong> means visitors to my portfolio or users of my demo applications.</li>
            <li><strong>Demo Applications</strong> are interactive projects I may showcase that collect user input.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies</strong> are small files placed on your device to enhance experience.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Collection -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Data Collection</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-800/30 p-4 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-white">What I Collect</h4>
            <p>My portfolio is designed to minimize data collection. Any information gathered falls into these categories:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
              <li><strong>Voluntary Information:</strong> Data you provide through contact forms or demo applications</li>
              <li><strong>Automatic Information:</strong> Basic analytics via GitHub Pages (IP address, browser type)</li>
              <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Only for essential functionality in demo projects</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gray-800/30 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-white">Tracking Technologies</h4>
            <p>I use minimal tracking only where necessary for demo applications:</p>
            <div class="mt-3 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="bg-gray-900/50 p-3 rounded">
                <p class="text-pink-500 text-sm">Essential Cookies</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Required for demo application functionality</p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-900/50 p-3 rounded">
                <p class="text-pink-500 text-sm">Session Storage</p>
                <p class="text-sm">Temporary data for your current visit</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- How I Use Data -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Use of Information</h2>
          <p>Any collected data is used exclusively for:</p>
          
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-3">
            <li><strong>Portfolio Functionality:</strong> Operating demo applications and interactive elements</li>
            <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Responding to your inquiries if you contact me</li>
            <li><strong>Improvements:</strong> Understanding how visitors use my portfolio to enhance it</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="mt-4 bg-gray-800/20 p-4 rounded border border-gray-700">
            <p class="text-sm"><span class="text-pink-400 font-medium">Important:</span> I don't sell, trade, or monetize your data in any way. This portfolio has no advertising or third-party tracking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Protection -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Security</h3>
          <p>I implement reasonable security measures appropriate for a personal portfolio:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
            <li>Minimal data collection principles</li>
            <li>Regular review of security practices</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm">Note: As this is hosted on GitHub Pages, please also review <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-privacy-statement" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300" target="_blank">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Third Parties -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>This portfolio may link to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>My professional profiles (GitHub, LinkedIn)</li>
            <li>Project demo deployments</li>
            <li>Technical documentation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">These services have their own privacy policies which I recommend reviewing.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Your Rights -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You can:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-1">
            <li>Request details about data I may have about you</li>
            <li>Ask for deletion of any personal information</li>
            <li>Disable cookies in your browser settings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Changes to Policy -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Policy Updates</h2>
          <p>I may update this policy occasionally. The "Last updated" date at the top will reflect changes.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <div class="bg-pink-900/20 p-6 rounded-xl border border-pink-900/50">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Contact Me</h2>
          <p>For any privacy-related questions:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2">
            <li>Email: <a href="mailto:albertoplazamontesdm@gmail.com" class="text-pink-400 hover:text-pink-300">albertoplazamontesdm@gmail.com</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>